k said, Garcia had access to the internal list guiding the distribution of =
Angel=E2=80=99s Envy Cask Strength, Old Fitzgerald 17-year Bottled in Bond,=
 WhistlePig 18-year Double Malt Rye and other sought-after bottles.


=E2=80=9CThey said, =E2=80=98Why don=E2=80=99t we make a little money on th=
e side,=E2=80=99 =E2=80=9D Stock alleged in an interview.
